{
  "stem": "13911.7",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It-- It was going like magic, then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you know, hopes were so high that eventually it will-- there-- there will be an end to it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because it seemed like this-- this war will never end.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, again, no place for thoughts or for dreams or-- no.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just existing, existing, and making the day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just actually-- yeah, this is what I'll say.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Living today.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Tomorrow?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who knows?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Who cares?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Who cares?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Who knows, tomorrow?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Living day by day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just that, oh yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, we still had that [POLISH], you should call it, or that concept, that tomorrow, tomorrow, what's tomorrow?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Today.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Only today.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even when were already in the free world.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we still-- maybe we didn't know any better.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were young.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had no means.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So whatever we had.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Today I was rich if I had $1 on me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Tomorrow, who knows?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, so we move on with the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we followed the-- the Russians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We'd you know, go right next-- follow them, until they liberate Wlodzimierz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we heard, already-- at that time, we could hear, already, you know, the Russians were there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were radios.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You could-- you-- you-- you knew what was happening in the world.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we have to go back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because where else do you go?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- but-- but where do you go?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where is it better?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Who wants you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You-- when you go, you have to have a-- a [? zeal-- ?] help-- help me out, maybe.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You have to have a-- a purpose or a-- how do you say it?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like, you know, a goal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm-- I'm-- I'm heading towards something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who wants me?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who needs me?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where do I belong?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No relatives, nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it's home.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
